{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"91113-le-jour-de-chance-d-hamisi","title":"Le Jour De Chance D’Hamisi!","description":"Hamisi goes to buy his uniform and spots a shirt he wants. His father says he doesn't have the money for it. What will happen to Hamisi's wish?","language":"French","langCode":"fr","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Nadine Verdier","Translators withoutBorders"],"illustrators":["Rob Owen"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"African Storybook Initiative","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/91113-le-jour-de-chance-d-hamisi"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/130943/size3/4301ba557d8658d098e9b0c3cde586a2.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/130943/size6/4301ba557d8658d098e9b0c3cde586a2.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128393/size6/3b814a22e04f94a3da806ed0d4bfe9e8.jpg","text":"Hamisi a besoin\nd'un nouvel\nuniforme scolaire.\nSon père l'emmène\nau marché.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128394/size6/526d93f337862dcf85f78b47d444097a.jpg","text":"Hamisi voit un\ngarçon vêtu d'une\nbelle chemise. \"Çac'est une belle\nchemise\" pense\nHamisi.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128395/size6/c59c72ae8fffa8e21438f443345eea50.jpg","text":"\"J'aimerais avoir\nune chemise\ncomme ce garçon\"\ndit Hamisi.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128396/size6/a9a1625a815da51dbf82493210caae90.jpg","text":"\" Regarde, elle\nvend ces chemises\nspéciales\" dit\nHamisi. \"Papa, s'il\nte plaît achète\nm'en une \"\ndemande-t-il.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128397/size6/a509b9803eb2d5fd1da587a898ab1346.jpg","text":"\"Hamisi, je dois\nacheter ton\nuniforme\" dit papa.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128398/size6/13af50e7aac54ba06c3c69893e6f116c.jpg","text":"\"Je n'ai pas assez\nd'argent pour cette\nchemise\" dit papa.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128399/size6/f9cdd8511bdc8140560b5916970beab3.jpg","text":"Le père d'Hamisi\npaie l'uniforme. Il\nest surpris\nlorsqu'on lui rend\nla monnaie. Il y a\nassez pour acheter\nune chemise!","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/128400/size6/f961da4690551e1359c0c43ef6106e8d.jpg","text":"C'est le jour de\nchance d'Hamisi!\nQuelle chemise va-t-\nil choisir?","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":8,"words":103}}